1
00:00:06,923 --> 00:00:09,426
I've had indigestion for a while now.

2
00:00:09,509 --> 00:00:11,177
Me too.

3
00:00:11,261 --> 00:00:12,470
- What is it?
- Oh, my God.

4
00:00:14,514 --> 00:00:16,474
CHOI HYUK-JOON HAS CHOSEN
AN JEONG-EUN

5
00:00:16,558 --> 00:00:18,435
What does that mean?

6
00:00:18,518 --> 00:00:21,312
- Oh, what will Hyun-seo do?
- Seriously. What will she do?

7
00:00:22,355 --> 00:00:24,274
This is really uncomfortable
for Jeong-eun too.

8
00:00:24,357 --> 00:00:25,650
I know, right?

9
00:00:25,734 --> 00:00:29,362
HAN SU-JI HAS CHOSEN
CHOI HYUK-JOON

10
00:00:29,988 --> 00:00:32,073
- Eh?
- What?

11
00:00:32,157 --> 00:00:35,035
- I don't think he can believe it.
- Ugh, I-I can't watch this.

12
00:00:35,118 --> 00:00:37,620
Are we allowed to choose
someone who's in there?

13
00:00:37,704 --> 00:00:39,998
- What is this?
- I'm taking off, guys.

14
00:00:40,081 --> 00:00:42,751
- I'll see you all later.
- Is this right? Hold on.

15
00:00:42,834 --> 00:00:44,169
Bye.

16
00:00:51,718 --> 00:00:54,345
Huh? Wait, what?

17
00:00:54,429 --> 00:00:57,057
What's this mean?
Three people are going in?

18
00:00:57,766 --> 00:00:58,933
- I guess so.
- I guess.

19
00:00:59,476 --> 00:01:00,894
Oh…

20
00:01:03,730 --> 00:01:05,148
- Oh!
- Jung-yun's in shock.

21
00:01:05,231 --> 00:01:07,358
And Hyun-seo's also quite shocked.

22
00:01:08,693 --> 00:01:11,696
Uh, I'm not thrilled, no.

23
00:01:11,780 --> 00:01:14,240
Because this isn't just any date.

24
00:01:14,324 --> 00:01:15,909
It's a Sparks House date,

25
00:01:15,992 --> 00:01:18,870
which I think has a lot of significance.

26
00:01:18,953 --> 00:01:22,165
But the problem is that
Su-ji also picked Hyuk-joon,

27
00:01:22,248 --> 00:01:24,459
which makes it two girls to one guy.

28
00:01:25,418 --> 00:01:28,338
So that's kind of aggravating.

29
00:01:28,421 --> 00:01:31,466
But fine. We'll have fun, the three of us.

30
00:01:36,638 --> 00:01:38,098
Oh, poor Jung-yun.

31
00:01:41,684 --> 00:01:45,063
I honest to God
did not see this coming at all.

32
00:01:45,146 --> 00:01:46,606
Not even a little bit.

33
00:01:46,689 --> 00:01:48,399
I did think for a moment…

34
00:01:50,026 --> 00:01:52,070
that I might be going,

35
00:01:52,153 --> 00:01:54,322
but Su-ji is really hard to read.

36
00:01:54,405 --> 00:01:56,783
So I have no idea what to expect.

37
00:01:58,368 --> 00:01:59,452
Oh, damn it.

38
00:02:01,329 --> 00:02:03,331
- What? What?
- Huh?

39
00:02:03,414 --> 00:02:05,458
What's this? Hold on, what is this?

40
00:02:05,542 --> 00:02:08,586
Look, I was going to explain.
Why did they have to reveal it like this?

41
00:02:08,670 --> 00:02:12,423
I was really surprised
that Hyuk-joon chose Jeong-eun,

42
00:02:12,507 --> 00:02:15,135
and I suddenly felt a little conflicted.

43
00:02:15,218 --> 00:02:18,638
My first solid choice was Jeong-eun.

44
00:02:18,721 --> 00:02:22,809
And it was around 6:00 p.m.
when I decided that.

45
00:02:22,892 --> 00:02:25,478
So when this happened,
only an hour and a half later,

46
00:02:25,562 --> 00:02:26,688
I was like, wow.

47
00:02:27,355 --> 00:02:28,565
I've never felt…

48
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:31,693
such emotional weight in my life.

49
00:02:34,904 --> 00:02:37,157
I'd never intended to face
a situation like that.

50
00:02:38,908 --> 00:02:42,287
I think this is going to be really hard.
I may need some alone time.

51
00:02:43,663 --> 00:02:46,332
WHO ARE YOU INTERESTED IN
RIGHT NOW?

52
00:02:47,041 --> 00:02:49,586
I think I may end up
being interested in Hyuk-joon,

53
00:02:49,669 --> 00:02:52,547
but at the same time, I'm becoming
more sure that I really like Jin-woo.

54
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:55,884
So right now, I'm confused…
in a good way, I guess.

55
00:02:55,967 --> 00:02:58,386
I never expected to see
my name there as his choice,

56
00:02:58,469 --> 00:03:00,597
so yeah, I was pleasantly surprised.

57
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:03,808
Since Jin-woo and I have already been
to Sparks House together,

58
00:03:03,892 --> 00:03:06,060
he knows what the vibe is like.

59
00:03:06,144 --> 00:03:08,730
So I know me going with Hyuk-joon
would bother him,

60
00:03:08,813 --> 00:03:11,024
and that weighed on my mind a little.

61
00:03:11,107 --> 00:03:14,152
- Sparks House is a little more intimate…
- Exactly, that's the point.

62
00:03:15,195 --> 00:03:16,487
Wait. Oh, wait.

63
00:03:23,786 --> 00:03:25,622
Man, this is crazy.

64
00:03:28,124 --> 00:03:29,667
I agonized over it.

65
00:03:29,751 --> 00:03:33,254
With Hyun-seo, we already had
many conversations.

66
00:03:33,338 --> 00:03:35,965
I honestly wondered
what more we could talk about

67
00:03:36,049 --> 00:03:37,300
if we went on another date.

68
00:03:37,383 --> 00:03:41,763
I felt like it would be a redo of
the conversations we already have had.

69
00:03:41,846 --> 00:03:44,015
And what more could be gained from it?

70
00:03:44,098 --> 00:03:46,476
So there was really no reason
to have another date.

71
00:03:46,559 --> 00:03:47,727
Ah!

72
00:03:47,810 --> 00:03:49,979
Oh, but it would be different.

73
00:03:50,063 --> 00:03:54,609
I really hesitated over whether
I should stay with my number one choice

74
00:03:54,692 --> 00:03:57,362
or have a one-on-one conversation
with another person

75
00:03:57,445 --> 00:03:59,155
I'm considering right now.

76
00:03:59,822 --> 00:04:01,866
Ultimately,
I decided to go with Jeong-eun.

77
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:04,244
I wanted to get to know her better

78
00:04:04,327 --> 00:04:07,705
because she chose me
in the 5 Minute Library,

79
00:04:07,789 --> 00:04:11,167
and she has this unique
positive energy about her.

80
00:04:11,793 --> 00:04:14,796
I thought it would be nice
to share an experience with her.

81
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:19,634
But then I saw the text
and learned that Su-ji had chosen me.

82
00:04:19,717 --> 00:04:22,887
I never expected her to make that choice,

83
00:04:23,513 --> 00:04:26,808
so yeah, I was really caught off guard.

84
00:04:27,433 --> 00:04:30,061
Okay, so they're free to choose

85
00:04:30,144 --> 00:04:32,897
who they go with to Sparks House,

86
00:04:33,398 --> 00:04:37,652
but I kind of feel like Hyuk-joon's
a little too into himself right now.

87
00:04:37,735 --> 00:04:40,488
He needs to get into her instead.
Oh, did I just say that?

88
00:04:41,322 --> 00:04:44,075
It really bothers me,
but you can't deny that he's popular.

89
00:04:44,158 --> 00:04:46,035
- Yeah, you're right.
- He is a catch.

90
00:04:46,119 --> 00:04:47,370
Definitely. He's a total catch.

91
00:04:48,746 --> 00:04:50,456
But why did they have to…

92
00:04:50,540 --> 00:04:52,709
- Did they have to reveal it like that?
- I know.

93
00:04:52,792 --> 00:04:55,503
Ugh, I'm so annoyed! No, no, this is fun.

94
00:04:55,586 --> 00:04:57,964
- Yeah, it's embarrassing.
- This is so fun.

95
00:04:58,047 --> 00:05:00,174
- I wonder what they're thinking.
- I…

96
00:05:00,258 --> 00:05:02,260
Actually, who cares, right?
No, I do care, I do care.

97
00:05:02,343 --> 00:05:04,178
- I care about what they're thinking.
- Really?

98
00:05:04,262 --> 00:05:07,473
I don't care right now, but I won't
be able to go to breakfast tomorrow.

99
00:05:07,557 --> 00:05:09,183
I definitely will need to explain myself.

100
00:05:09,267 --> 00:05:11,644
Like, "Guys, I actually
wanted to have conversations

101
00:05:11,728 --> 00:05:12,895
with both of them, damn it."

102
00:05:12,979 --> 00:05:14,188
I really did.

103
00:05:14,272 --> 00:05:16,607
- Yeah. That's how she really feels.
- Yeah.

104
00:05:16,691 --> 00:05:20,570
I was totally
expecting this to cause a big stir.

105
00:05:20,653 --> 00:05:22,280
Well, I get that.

106
00:05:22,363 --> 00:05:25,867
But I didn't like how everyone assumed

107
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:28,536
that I would go with Jung-yun.

108
00:05:28,619 --> 00:05:31,205
Why were they making
such assumptions about me?

109
00:05:31,289 --> 00:05:33,249
I was like,
"Hey, my second choice is Hyuk-joon,

110
00:05:33,333 --> 00:05:35,460
and I'm also interested
in my second choice."

111
00:05:35,543 --> 00:05:37,170
I'm also into hiking.

112
00:05:37,253 --> 00:05:39,380
You know, that's a weird coincidence.

113
00:05:39,881 --> 00:05:42,008
My favorite hobby is hiking.

114
00:05:42,091 --> 00:05:45,345
- Don't lie to me. Seriously, stop lying.
- Seriously. No, seriously.

115
00:05:45,428 --> 00:05:48,806
Well, my attraction to my top pick
has actually taken a hit.

116
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,642
Wow. We sure think alike.

117
00:05:51,726 --> 00:05:52,977
They're on the same wavelength.

118
00:05:53,061 --> 00:05:55,313
Hey, are you feeling okay?
I heard you're sick.

119
00:05:55,396 --> 00:05:56,481
Yeah, I'm okay.

120
00:05:56,564 --> 00:05:57,982
I'm not sure you are.

121
00:05:58,649 --> 00:05:59,859
You don't look okay.

122
00:06:00,610 --> 00:06:01,611
Oh, no.

123
00:06:02,278 --> 00:06:05,698
Of course I was worried about
what Jung-yun would think.

124
00:06:06,407 --> 00:06:07,950
But what can I do?

125
00:06:08,034 --> 00:06:10,953
I really thought I needed to have
a conversation with Hyuk-joon.

126
00:06:11,037 --> 00:06:12,663
And I'm only human,

127
00:06:12,747 --> 00:06:15,541
so I couldn't help but be
a little concerned about Hyun-seo

128
00:06:15,625 --> 00:06:19,128
constantly talking about Hyuk-joon
and expressing interest.

129
00:06:19,670 --> 00:06:23,633
I did wonder if I was getting
in the way of their relationship,

130
00:06:23,716 --> 00:06:25,551
and I didn't want to do that.

131
00:06:25,635 --> 00:06:27,678
But I wanted to find out for sure.

132
00:06:27,762 --> 00:06:31,516
This opportunity had fallen into my lap,
so why wouldn't I take advantage of it?

133
00:06:31,599 --> 00:06:35,395
I do wish she'd talked this through
before going off to Sparks House, though.

134
00:06:35,478 --> 00:06:38,106
- As in, "I'm curious about him," right?
- "I'm kind of curious about him."

135
00:06:38,189 --> 00:06:40,441
"I'm going to keep things open
and have a conversation with him."

136
00:06:40,525 --> 00:06:42,568
Wouldn't it have been better
if she'd said that before going?

137
00:06:44,654 --> 00:06:46,155
This isn't a typo?

138
00:06:46,823 --> 00:06:48,241
Is it actually possible?

139
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,662
I don't think…

140
00:07:03,297 --> 00:07:07,009
I can't really wrap my head around
what's going on with either of them.

141
00:07:08,177 --> 00:07:09,220
I don't know.

142
00:07:11,097 --> 00:07:12,890
Oh, no. I can't watch this.

143
00:07:17,395 --> 00:07:18,771
- Hey, there. Hello.
- Hello.

144
00:07:18,855 --> 00:07:19,981
It's these guys again.

145
00:07:20,064 --> 00:07:23,276
Yeah, these are the guys that
knew Su-ji would be all in on Jung-yun.

146
00:07:23,359 --> 00:07:24,444
What?

147
00:07:24,527 --> 00:07:26,612
Did you come to see how I was doing?

148
00:07:26,696 --> 00:07:28,406
No.

149
00:07:28,489 --> 00:07:30,575
I'm here because
I'm a bit bothered at the moment.

150
00:07:30,658 --> 00:07:31,742
Yeah, I bet.

151
00:07:31,826 --> 00:07:36,247
But really, what right do we have
to judge their choices?

152
00:07:36,330 --> 00:07:39,041
- Yeah, you're right. That's a good point.
- Yeah, really.

153
00:07:39,709 --> 00:07:42,587
- But I do need to get to the bottom of it.
- Right.

154
00:07:42,670 --> 00:07:46,048
I mean, I was honest and direct
in expressing my feelings to her.

155
00:07:46,132 --> 00:07:48,301
And the response I'm receiving

156
00:07:49,302 --> 00:07:50,678
feels like rejection.

157
00:07:50,761 --> 00:07:53,848
Because it's not like
she hasn't been to Sparks House.

158
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:58,519
So she knows
a conversation isn't possible.

159
00:07:58,603 --> 00:08:01,272
She's been to Sparks House,
she's been there before,

160
00:08:01,355 --> 00:08:02,857
so she knows that.

161
00:08:03,524 --> 00:08:06,068
It's disappointing that she…

162
00:08:07,361 --> 00:08:09,655
couldn't at least give me a heads-up.

163
00:08:11,449 --> 00:08:12,658
Yeah, I get that.

164
00:08:14,243 --> 00:08:16,329
And she must've known
when she chose him, right?

165
00:08:16,412 --> 00:08:18,956
Yeah, she had to have known.

166
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,166
Yeah.

167
00:08:20,249 --> 00:08:23,211
- It's been less than half a day.
- Less than half a day, and I just--

168
00:08:23,294 --> 00:08:25,296
Switching out of the blue
is kind of messed up.

169
00:08:26,506 --> 00:08:29,675
Oh, so Su-ji told Jung-yun
they would talk this evening,

170
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:32,386
but now instead of doing that,
she's going off to Sparks House.

171
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:35,306
- Just the two of them.
- They can't talk if she's at Sparks House.

172
00:08:35,389 --> 00:08:37,850
He's going to make life harder for
himself if he gets hung up on that.

173
00:08:37,934 --> 00:08:41,062
Yeah, Jung-yun shouldn't treat this
like it's the end of the road.

174
00:08:41,145 --> 00:08:43,648
Jung-yun's reading too much into this.

175
00:08:43,731 --> 00:08:45,024
Yeah, I think so too.

176
00:08:45,107 --> 00:08:46,734
This is the second time today.

177
00:08:46,817 --> 00:08:47,777
SPARKS HOUSE

178
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:48,778
Oh!

179
00:08:48,861 --> 00:08:50,404
- Hello.
- Hello.

180
00:08:50,488 --> 00:08:52,782
The star of the day.

181
00:08:52,865 --> 00:08:55,868
You're killing it.
You're an alpha male, all right?

182
00:08:55,952 --> 00:08:57,828
- What's all this?
- Come sit in the middle.

183
00:08:57,912 --> 00:08:59,997
- Oh, sure, sure.
- Yeah, sit in the middle.

184
00:09:00,081 --> 00:09:01,249
You're the guest of honor.

185
00:09:05,044 --> 00:09:06,671
This is truly a feast.

186
00:09:08,172 --> 00:09:10,550
Why don't you tell us
how you feel while we eat?

187
00:09:10,633 --> 00:09:12,385
It's your idea. Why don't you start?

188
00:09:12,468 --> 00:09:14,011
- Okay, so for me…
- Yeah?

189
00:09:14,095 --> 00:09:17,056
- …I only had two options from the start.
- Okay.

190
00:09:17,139 --> 00:09:19,433
And that was you and Jung-yun.

191
00:09:19,517 --> 00:09:21,561
You see, Su-ji is definitely frank.

192
00:09:21,644 --> 00:09:24,355
But I had a bit of a conversation
with Jung-yun today.

193
00:09:24,438 --> 00:09:26,190
And I felt like so far I had focused

194
00:09:26,274 --> 00:09:28,651
a little too much
on getting to know Jung-yun.

195
00:09:28,734 --> 00:09:30,861
That's why I've been
wanting to talk with you,

196
00:09:30,945 --> 00:09:33,990
to get to know you better,
but I just haven't had the opportunity.

197
00:09:34,490 --> 00:09:37,451
So I just thought, "I don't know.
I'll just go with the flow."

198
00:09:37,535 --> 00:09:38,869
And that's what I did.

199
00:09:38,953 --> 00:09:40,121
- Right.
- Yeah.

200
00:09:40,204 --> 00:09:42,331
And now you two are sitting awfully close.

201
00:09:45,418 --> 00:09:47,211
The way he's looking at her… Huh?

202
00:09:47,295 --> 00:09:50,423
Whoa, he's looking at her like that
from a short a distance?

203
00:09:52,341 --> 00:09:54,510
I'm feeling kind of uncomfortable.

204
00:09:54,594 --> 00:09:56,637
- Could you stop looking at me?
- Oh, sure. Sorry.

205
00:09:58,097 --> 00:10:00,933
Is this the first time
we're seeing Su-ji feeling uncomfortable?

206
00:10:01,017 --> 00:10:02,768
I think it's because she's feeling shy.

207
00:10:02,852 --> 00:10:04,979
But at this point,
his first choice is Jeong-eun.

208
00:10:05,062 --> 00:10:06,981
Hopefully, now that he's here,

209
00:10:07,064 --> 00:10:09,066
Hyuk-joon can satisfy
his curiosity about Jeong-eun.

210
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:10,901
But how is this conversation
going to work?

211
00:10:10,985 --> 00:10:11,819
I know, right?

212
00:10:11,902 --> 00:10:14,113
- How about you?
- Mmm, for me…

213
00:10:17,491 --> 00:10:19,535
- To be completely honest…
- Awkward. Right.

214
00:10:19,619 --> 00:10:22,663
…I've also, uh, been talking

215
00:10:23,289 --> 00:10:25,082
a lot with Hyun-seo,

216
00:10:25,166 --> 00:10:27,585
so I kind of thought it would be good

217
00:10:27,668 --> 00:10:30,379
to have a conversation
with Jeong-eun today.

218
00:10:30,463 --> 00:10:33,049
To be honest, I thought your mind
was pretty much made up.

219
00:10:33,132 --> 00:10:35,009
- Me too.
- That's what everyone thought.

220
00:10:35,092 --> 00:10:37,345
I thought your mind was made up too,
until earlier.

221
00:10:37,428 --> 00:10:39,972
- No, it's far from made up.
- I thought there was a huge gap.

222
00:10:40,056 --> 00:10:43,351
I thought that was the case too,
but talking to her…

223
00:10:43,851 --> 00:10:46,103
I kind of got this feeling

224
00:10:46,646 --> 00:10:50,941
that there was this kind of wall
forming between us.

225
00:10:51,025 --> 00:10:53,569
And it's felt that way
for a day or two now.

226
00:10:53,653 --> 00:10:54,487
Mm-hmm.

227
00:10:54,570 --> 00:10:58,824
So this time, I wanted to make
my own choice and do something new.

228
00:10:58,908 --> 00:11:00,368
He's leaving the door open.

229
00:11:00,451 --> 00:11:03,412
Two, actually.
He's leaving a door open for both of them.

230
00:11:03,496 --> 00:11:05,831
I may have to go on tour.

231
00:11:05,915 --> 00:11:08,376
I'm just too interested in all of them.

232
00:11:08,459 --> 00:11:09,752
"Go on tour"?

233
00:11:09,835 --> 00:11:12,380
- That came across as really cocky.
- What did he say?

234
00:11:12,463 --> 00:11:15,675
I mean, what, is this guy drunk right now?

235
00:11:17,218 --> 00:11:19,053
It definitely looks
like he's been drinking.

236
00:11:19,136 --> 00:11:21,055
I don't know.
Maybe he is actually just drunk.

237
00:11:21,138 --> 00:11:24,642
Uh, I did actually tell Hyun-seo
in advance

238
00:11:24,725 --> 00:11:27,728
that I was still interested
in talking to the others.

239
00:11:27,812 --> 00:11:28,813
ROTATION DATES

240
00:11:28,896 --> 00:11:31,565
Well, it seems as far as having
